  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nNoticed a few times - especially reproducible on goerli.\r\nThere are situations when Old Headers are getting stucked in the middle of process and are not progressing in any way. This cannot be CL related so seems like some networking issue or we lost peers for Headers and unable to restore them.\r\n\r\n**Desktop (please complete the following information):**\r\n - OS: Ubuntu\r\n - Chain: goerli\r\n - Version: master\r\n\r\n**Debug Logs**\r\n[goerli.logs (2).zip](https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/files/10231498/goerli.logs.2.zip)\r\n\r\n",
